{"segment_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation", "source_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "城內塹外周道，廣八步，備水謹度四旁高下。", "text_normalized": "城內塹外周道，廣八步，備水謹度四旁高下。", "canonical_ref": "45.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation", "source_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "城地中偏下，令耳亓內，及下地，地深穿之令漏泉。", "text_normalized": "城地中偏下，令耳亓內，及下地，地深穿之令漏泉。", "canonical_ref": "45.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation", "source_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "置則瓦井中，視外水深丈以上，鑿城內水耳。", "text_normalized": "置則瓦井中，視外水深丈以上，鑿城內水耳。", "canonical_ref": "45.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation", "source_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "並船以為十臨，臨三十人，人擅弩計四有方，必善以船為轒轀。", "text_normalized": "並船以為十臨，臨三十人，人擅弩計四有方，必善以船為轒轀。", "canonical_ref": "45.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation", "source_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "二十船為一隊，選材士有力者三十人共船，亓二十人人擅有方，劍甲鞮瞀，十人人擅苗。", "text_normalized": "二十船為一隊，選材士有力者三十人共船，亓二十人人擅有方，劍甲鞮瞀，十人人擅苗。", "canonical_ref": "45.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation", "source_id": "mozi-045-preparation-against-inundation__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "先養材士為異舍，食亓父母妻子以為質，視水可決，以臨轒轀，決外隄，城上為射機疾佐之。", "text_normalized": "先養材士為異舍，食亓父母妻子以為質，視水可決，以臨轒轀，決外隄，城上為射機疾佐之。", "canonical_ref": "45.6", "notes": ""}
